#                                                                                                                                                                                                       

[media]

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

[media]

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

[media]

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

[media]

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

[media]

**Christmas Update**
- New Xmas Battlepass
- Christmas Ornament Hunt
- New Rudolf Bundle
- Christmas Themed Levels

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/499303746_2181339939044468_540727540857874572_n.mp4?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=GfymLvk-PtYQ7kNvwHcdiL2&_nc_oc=AdnmKe3xJFAg6DxeC8qLfMA3oSwuekLHTzvSC7DOH6ikr8BuuysJ_CXXGFJSrsiOwL4&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=n4BWw8hYR_Lv2WjX47kV2A&oh=00_AfrQzYtapaP_624EtNkHabgu27MTg0dP4TRKKILTpQUmjw&oe=696F10A4)

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491830888_1234204841304584_7133986973260987280_n.mp4?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=H-twqA3ow68Q7kNvwFs-rOt&_nc_oc=Adkq2JLHp2zhUwDyh0qv4A8xEaSpoAbomjqtH6xTGQP2EmsS_mtZvVSI4R1_SYniXag&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=n4BWw8hYR_Lv2WjX47kV2A&oh=00_AfrUsVitJy2TaarkfpLqiBYpak5DqaWWyGxX6aMref5BSQ&oe=696F16FC)

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491821117_1430846481437060_8099142216261706884_n.mp4?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=oHpKOvFRvYAQ7kNvwHtRGAK&_nc_oc=AdlLSrkq2n8wbXqODZsH8wdsXgXBYQksvOwU8bbdSKafJiMvJeBWYi9I5FYt_wldCts&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=n4BWw8hYR_Lv2WjX47kV2A&oh=00_AfqlGX10OY8JhzyACDSSyPdKLeg25Q05pUfvXeRvYzU02w&oe=696F05CC)

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

![{"height":1440,"type":"image","width":2560}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/499292426_757548860702625_520424425045914625_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7cX7M8kESW0Q7kNvwGmMXXx&_nc_oc=AdkB5XiL8MS7mh91p7PzUFeHUBOkIfhVBrkaLsaPFyQJZGD2LgZVHk7x3UN8eE3cL9o&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_Afr8JHneH2ttzzqvBMm1WKRG52JJoaAo_2yxbLSZb8lwFw&oe=696F0332)
